const _astro_dataLayerContent = [["Map",1,2,9,10,41,42],"meta::meta",["Map",3,4,5,6,7,8],"astro-version","5.11.0","content-config-digest","b3037754b9aef6f7","astro-config-digest","{\"root\":{},\"srcDir\":{},\"publicDir\":{},\"outDir\":{},\"cacheDir\":{},\"compressHTML\":true,\"base\":\"/\",\"trailingSlash\":\"ignore\",\"output\":\"server\",\"scopedStyleStrategy\":\"attribute\",\"build\":{\"format\":\"directory\",\"client\":{},\"server\":{},\"assets\":\"_astro\",\"serverEntry\":\"entry.mjs\",\"redirects\":false,\"inlineStylesheets\":\"auto\",\"concurrency\":1},\"server\":{\"open\":false,\"host\":false,\"port\":4321,\"streaming\":true,\"allowedHosts\":[]},\"redirects\":{},\"image\":{\"endpoint\":{\"route\":\"/_image\"},\"service\":{\"entrypoint\":\"astro/assets/services/sharp\",\"config\":{}},\"domains\":[],\"remotePatterns\":[],\"responsiveStyles\":false},\"devToolbar\":{\"enabled\":true},\"markdown\":{\"syntaxHighlight\":{\"type\":\"shiki\",\"excludeLangs\":[\"math\"]},\"shikiConfig\":{\"langs\":[],\"langAlias\":{},\"theme\":\"github-dark\",\"themes\":{},\"wrap\":false,\"transformers\":[]},\"remarkPlugins\":[],\"rehypePlugins\":[],\"remarkRehype\":{},\"gfm\":true,\"smartypants\":true},\"security\":{\"checkOrigin\":true},\"env\":{\"schema\":{},\"validateSecrets\":false},\"experimental\":{\"clientPrerender\":false,\"contentIntellisense\":false,\"headingIdCompat\":false,\"preserveScriptOrder\":false,\"liveContentCollections\":false,\"csp\":false},\"legacy\":{\"collections\":false},\"session\":{\"driver\":\"fs-lite\",\"options\":{\"base\":\"/Users/nasifsalaam/Documents/GitHub/Astro-portfolio-24/node_modules/.astro/sessions\"}}}","blog",["Map",11,12,28,29],"journey-from-design-to-development-ai-shift",{id:11,data:13,body:23,filePath:24,digest:25,legacyId:26,deferredRender:27},{title:14,description:15,pubDate:16,image:17,tags:18},"The Journey from Design to Development: Embracing the AI-Driven Shift","A personal perspective on how AI is transforming the traditional boundaries between design and development roles",["Date","2024-11-03T00:00:00.000Z"],"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1597239450996-ea7c2c564412?q=80&w=987&auto=format&fit=crop&ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D",[19,20,21,22],"AI","Design","Development","Career","The current state of design and development is shifting rapidly, largely due to the advent of AI. This technological revolution is reshaping the roles of designers and developers, blurring the lines between these once distinct disciplines. AI is taking over significant portions of design work in UX and UI, while also making inroads into development. Although we're not yet at a stage where AI-generated solutions are fully refined, these tools are enabling designers and developers to work in fundamentally new ways.\n\nAs a designer with a longstanding interest in code, I've seen firsthand how AI is bridging the gap between design and development. While I've always had some familiarity with HTML and CSS, the current AI-powered toolset is making it possible for designers like me to become truly cross-functional professionals.\n\n## The Shift Towards Development: A Designer's Perspective\n\nThe tech space is evolving at breakneck speed, and design is no exception. AI has upended traditional paradigms, emphasizing the need for creativity, user empathy, and critical thinking in both design and development roles. As designers, we're increasingly exposed to the possibilities and constraints of development, making it natural to gravitate in that direction.\n\n<div class=\"text-lg text-muted-foreground mb-6\">\n  I became a designer due to my passion for creativity, initially viewing development as a highly technical skill that was outside my wheelhouse. However, in recent years, I've found myself contemplating development more and more.\n</div>\n\nAI has provided a sort of \"cheat code,\" allowing designers to explore their designs in code through simple prompts. While it's true that AI-generated code can be buggy, it's crucial to remember that we're witnessing these tools at their worst – they will only improve from here.\n\n## The Age of Visual Development\n\nLow-code and no-code tools like FlutterFlow, Webflow, Framer, Draftbit, and Plasmic are further bridging the gap between design and development. Even before the AI boom, these tools had gained popularity, but AI has supercharged their capabilities.\n\nThese visual development platforms have been invaluable in allowing designers to venture further into the production side of projects. With AI integration, their potential has expanded exponentially, opening up new possibilities for designer-developers.\n\n## Why Designers Should Care\n\n<div class=\"space-y-2 my-4 ml-6\">\n  <div class=\"flex items-start\">\n    <span class=\"text-primary mr-2\">•</span>\n    <span>Bringing Ideas to Life: Designers now have the power to design something and see it come to life quickly</span>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"flex items-start\">\n    <span class=\"text-primary mr-2\">•</span>\n    <span>Informed Design: Understanding the development process allows designers to create more feasible designs</span>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"flex items-start\">\n    <span class=\"text-primary mr-2\">•</span>\n    <span>Enhanced Collaboration: Speaking the language of developers improves communication</span>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"flex items-start\">\n    <span class=\"text-primary mr-2\">•</span>\n    <span>Career Opportunities: Designer-developers are in high demand</span>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n## The AI Factor\n\n<div class=\"text-xl text-primary/90 italic my-8 pl-6 border-l-4 border-primary\">\n  AI is the real game-changer in this transition. Tools like ChatGPT and Claude are making it significantly easier to understand coding concepts, debug issues, and create high-fidelity prototypes.\n</div>\n\n## Making the Transition: From Design to Development\n\nFor designers looking to expand their skillset into development, here are some steps to consider:\n\n<div class=\"space-y-3 my-6 ml-6\">\n  <div class=\"flex items-start\">\n    <span class=\"text-primary font-bold mr-3\">1.</span>\n    <span>Start with Visual Development Tools: Platforms like Webflow or Framer offer a low barrier to entry</span>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"flex items-start\">\n    <span class=\"text-primary font-bold mr-3\">2.</span>\n    <span>Learn the Basics: Pick up fundamental web technologies like HTML and CSS</span>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"flex items-start\">\n    <span class=\"text-primary font-bold mr-3\">3.</span>\n    <span>Embrace AI: Leverage AI tools to learn, solve problems, and enhance your workflow</span>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"flex items-start\">\n    <span class=\"text-primary font-bold mr-3\">4.</span>\n    <span>Build Real Projects: Nothing beats hands-on experience</span>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"flex items-start\">\n    <span class=\"text-primary font-bold mr-3\">5.</span>\n    <span>Maintain Your Design Skills: Create projects from start to finish</span>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n## The Future is Hybrid\n\nWhile not every designer needs to become a full-stack developer (and vice versa), those designers with technical aptitude will find significant advantages in bridging the gap between design and development. As AI continues to develop, understanding how designs come to life in code may become a necessity for designers.\n\nThe challenges posed by AI also bring numerous opportunities. By adjusting our mindset to be opportunity-driven, we can navigate this shifting terrain and emerge as more versatile, valuable professionals in the world of design and development.","src/content/blog/journey-from-design-to-development-ai-shift.mdx","b38148abb676243a","journey-from-design-to-development-ai-shift.mdx",true,"visual-development-nocode-tools-transforming-design",{id:28,data:30,body:37,filePath:38,digest:39,legacyId:40,deferredRender:27},{title:31,description:32,pubDate:33,image:34,tags:35},"Visual Development: How No-Code Tools Are Transforming Digital Design","How artificial intelligence is transforming design workflows and creative processes",["Date","2024-11-10T00:00:00.000Z"],"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1547658719-da2b51169166?q=80&w=928&auto=format&fit=crop&ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D",[19,20,36],"Technology","The design world is changing rapidly, and I've been watching (and participating in) a fascinating shift in how we create digital products. Visual development tools are fundamentally changing what's possible for designers, and after spending significant time with these tools, I can tell you – this is more than just another trend.\n\n## Beyond the Static Canvas\n\nLet's be honest – we've all been there. You spend weeks perfecting a design in Figma or Sketch, only to wait months to see it actually working. This gap between design and reality has always frustrated me, and it's why I've become so excited about visual development platforms like FlutterFlow, Plasmic, Draftbit, Webflow, and Framer.\n\nThese tools aren't just another way to make prototypes; they're changing how we think about design implementation. Recently, I was working on a mobile app's login screen, and instead of just designing how it should look, I could actually test real keyboard interactions, validate input fields, and see exactly how the interface responded to different states. It's the difference between drawing a car and actually taking it for a test drive.\n\n## The Hidden Superpower: Understanding Data\n\nHere's something that surprised me – working with visual development tools has taught me more about data modeling than years of traditional design work. When you're building in these platforms, you have to think about how information flows through your application. This isn't just theoretical; it's practical knowledge that has completely changed how I approach design problems.\n\nFor example, when designing a user profile screen now, I'm not just thinking about the layout – I'm considering:\n\n<div class=\"space-y-2 my-4 ml-6\">\n  <div class=\"flex items-start\">\n    <span class=\"text-primary mr-2\">•</span>\n    <span>How the data connects to other parts of the app</span>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"flex items-start\">\n    <span class=\"text-primary mr-2\">•</span>\n    <span>Where information is stored and retrieved</span>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"flex items-start\">\n    <span class=\"text-primary mr-2\">•</span>\n    <span>How state changes affect different components</span>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"flex items-start\">\n    <span class=\"text-primary mr-2\">•</span>\n    <span>What happens during loading states</span>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\nThis understanding has made my conversations with developers so much more productive. Instead of throwing designs over the wall, we can have meaningful discussions about implementation.\n\n## AI: Your New Design Partner\n\nLet's talk about the elephant in the room – AI. It's everywhere now, and in visual development, it's actually becoming incredibly useful. I use AI not to replace my design thinking but to handle the mundane stuff: generating starting points, automating repetitive tasks, and getting quick code suggestions. This leaves more time for solving the real, human problems in our designs.\n\n## Real Results: From Months to Weeks\n\n<div class=\"text-lg text-muted-foreground mb-6\">\n  I recently led a team that built a functional app in about a month using FlutterFlow and AI – something that would have taken several months traditionally. But here's what really struck me: it wasn't just about speed.\n</div>\n\nThe team was more engaged because they could see their work coming to life immediately. There's something powerful about being able to test and iterate on real, working features instead of static mockups.\n\n## Moving Forward\n\nThe design industry is evolving, and we need to evolve with it. This doesn't mean abandoning our design principles or creative thinking. Instead, it's about augmenting our capabilities with new tools that help us create better, more realistic designs faster.\n\nFor designers wondering how to get started, my advice is simple:\n\n<div class=\"space-y-3 my-6 ml-6\">\n  <div class=\"flex items-start\">\n    <span class=\"text-primary font-bold mr-3\">1.</span>\n    <span>Start small – pick a simple project you've already designed</span>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"flex items-start\">\n    <span class=\"text-primary font-bold mr-3\">2.</span>\n    <span>Get comfortable with data concepts</span>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"flex items-start\">\n    <span class=\"text-primary font-bold mr-3\">3.</span>\n    <span>Use AI as a tool, not a crutch</span>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"flex items-start\">\n    <span class=\"text-primary font-bold mr-3\">4.</span>\n    <span>Focus on building real, working features</span>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"flex items-start\">\n    <span class=\"text-primary font-bold mr-3\">5.</span>\n    <span>Stay curious and keep experimenting</span>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n## The Future is Already Here\n\n<div class=\"text-xl text-primary/90 italic my-8 pl-6 border-l-4 border-primary\">\n  The future of design isn't about choosing between being a designer or a developer – it's about embracing tools that let us do both better.\n</div>\n\nWhat excites me most about visual development isn't just what it can do today – it's where it's heading. As these tools continue to evolve, the line between design and development is blurring in the best possible way. We're entering an era where designers can truly bring their visions to life without losing the craft and creativity that drew us to design in the first place.","src/content/blog/visual-development-nocode-tools-transforming-design.mdx","1fd86cfd16f86117","visual-development-nocode-tools-transforming-design.mdx","projects",["Map",43,44,59,60,74,75,87,88,102,103,117,118,132,133],"ai-powered-bike-app",{id:43,data:45,body:55,filePath:56,digest:57,legacyId:58,deferredRender:27},{title:46,description:47,image:48,tags:49,featured:54,published:54},"AI-Powered Bike App","Designed an innovative bike-sharing application that uses AI to optimize user experience and fleet management.","/images/placeholder.png",[50,51,52,53],"AI/ML","Mobile App","UX Design","Innovation",false,"import ClickableImage from '../../components/ClickableImage.astro';\nimport ContactButton from '../../components/ContactButton.astro';\n\n<div class=\"prose prose-lg max-w-none\">\n\n## Project Overview\nLed the design of an innovative bike-sharing application that leverages AI to enhance user experience and optimize fleet management. The project focused on creating an intuitive interface while incorporating complex AI features for predictive maintenance and smart routing.\n\n## Tools & Technologies\n<div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-4 my-6\">\n  <div class=\"inline-flex items-center px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-accent/10 text-sm\">\n    <span class=\"font-medium\">Design:</span>\n    <span class=\"ml-2\">Figma</span>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"inline-flex items-center px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-accent/10 text-sm\">\n    <span class=\"font-medium\">Prototyping:</span>\n    <span class=\"ml-2\">Principle</span>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"inline-flex items-center px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-accent/10 text-sm\">\n    <span class=\"font-medium\">Research:</span>\n    <span class=\"ml-2\">Miro</span>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n## The Challenge\n\n<div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6 my-8\">\n  <div class=\"relative overflow-hidden rounded-xl bg-card p-6 border border-primary/40\">\n    <div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary/10 via-primary/5 to-transparent\"></div>\n    <h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold mb-3 relative z-10\">Complex AI Integration</h3>\n    <p class=\"relative z-10\">Making advanced AI features accessible and intuitive for everyday users while maintaining system reliability.</p>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"relative overflow-hidden rounded-xl bg-card p-6 border border-primary/40\">\n    <div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary/10 via-primary/5 to-transparent\"></div>\n    <h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold mb-3 relative z-10\">Real-time Updates</h3>\n    <p class=\"relative z-10\">Displaying live data and predictions while maintaining app performance and battery efficiency.</p>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"relative overflow-hidden rounded-xl bg-card p-6 border border-primary/40\">\n    <div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary/10 via-primary/5 to-transparent\"></div>\n    <h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold mb-3 relative z-10\">User Trust</h3>\n    <p class=\"relative z-10\">Building confidence in AI-powered recommendations and predictions through transparent and reliable features.</p>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"relative overflow-hidden rounded-xl bg-card p-6 border border-primary/40\">\n    <div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary/10 via-primary/5 to-transparent\"></div>\n    <h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold mb-3 relative z-10\">Safety Integration</h3>\n    <p class=\"relative z-10\">Incorporating safety features without compromising user experience or adding complexity.</p>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n## Role & Responsibilities\n<ul class=\"list-none space-y-3  [&>li]:before:text-purple-600 [&>li]:before:mr-2 [&>li]:flex\">\n  <li>Led UX/UI design for the mobile application</li>\n  <li>Collaborated with AI engineers on feature integration</li>\n  <li>Conducted user research and testing</li>\n  <li>Created interactive prototypes</li>\n  <li>Developed design specifications</li>\n  <li>Managed design implementation with developers</li>\n</ul>\n\n## Key Features\n\n### Smart Features\nThe app incorporates several AI-powered features to enhance the bike-sharing experience:\n\n<ul class=\"list-none space-y-3 [&>li]:before:content-['•'] [&>li]:before:text-purple-600 [&>li]:before:mr-2 [&>li]:flex\">\n  <li>Predictive Availability - AI algorithms analyze historical data and real-time usage patterns to predict bike availability at different stations throughout the day.</li>\n  <li>Smart Routing - Personalized route suggestions based on user preferences, traffic conditions, and bike availability. The system learns from user behavior to improve recommendations over time.</li>\n  <li>Maintenance Alerts - Proactive maintenance notifications using AI analysis of bike sensor data to predict potential issues before they affect service.</li>\n  <li>Safety Monitoring - Real-time safety features including emergency assistance, route hazard detection, and automated incident reporting.</li>\n</ul>\n\n## Results & Impact\n\n<div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6 my-8\">\n  <div class=\"relative overflow-hidden rounded-xl bg-card p-6 border border-primary/40\">\n    <div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary/10 via-primary/5 to-transparent\"></div>\n    <h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold mb-3 relative z-10\">User Growth</h3>\n    <p class=\"relative z-10\">45% increase in active users within 3 months of launch, with particularly strong adoption among commuters.</p>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"relative overflow-hidden rounded-xl bg-card p-6 border border-primary/40\">\n    <div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary/10 via-primary/5 to-transparent\"></div>\n    <h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold mb-3 relative z-10\">Efficiency Gains</h3>\n    <p class=\"relative z-10\">30% improvement in bike utilization rates through optimized distribution and predictive analytics.</p>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"relative overflow-hidden rounded-xl bg-card p-6 border border-primary/40\">\n    <div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary/10 via-primary/5 to-transparent\"></div>\n    <h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold mb-3 relative z-10\">User Satisfaction</h3>\n    <p class=\"relative z-10\">4.8/5 average app rating with 10k+ reviews, highlighting the intuitive design and reliable predictions.</p>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"relative overflow-hidden rounded-xl bg-card p-6 border border-primary/40\">\n    <div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary/10 via-primary/5 to-transparent\"></div>\n    <h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold mb-3 relative z-10\">Maintenance Impact</h3>\n    <p class=\"relative z-10\">25% reduction in maintenance costs through predictive maintenance and optimized service scheduling.</p>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n## Key Learnings\n<ul class=\"list-none space-y-3 [&>li]:before:content-['•'] [&>li]:before:text-purple-600 [&>li]:before:mr-2 [&>li]:flex\">\n  <li>AI features need clear, intuitive interfaces to be effective</li>\n  <li>Real-time data must be presented thoughtfully to avoid overwhelming users</li>\n  <li>User trust in AI systems builds gradually through consistent performance</li>\n  <li>Safety features should be seamlessly integrated into the core experience</li>\n  <li>Regular user feedback is crucial for AI feature refinement</li>\n  <li>Balance between automation and user control is essential</li>\n</ul>\n\n<div class=\"not-prose mt-8\">\n  <ContactButton />\n</div>\n\n</div>","src/content/projects/ai-powered-bike-app.mdx","adb28b32a8e2bed6","ai-powered-bike-app.mdx","enterprise-design-system",{id:59,data:61,body:70,filePath:71,digest:72,legacyId:73,deferredRender:27},{title:62,description:63,image:64,tags:65,featured:54,published:27},"Enterprise Design System","Created a comprehensive design system for a South African financial institution, enabling consistent user experiences.","/images/card 01 - design.jpg",[66,67,68,69],"Design Systems","UI Design","Documentation","Financial Services","import ClickableImage from '../../components/ClickableImage.astro';\nimport ContactButton from '../../components/ContactButton.astro';\n\n<div class=\"prose prose-lg max-w-none\">\n\n## Project Overview\nA South African financial institution needed a comprehensive design system to ensure consistency across their digital products while enabling rapid development and scaling. As Senior UI Designer, I architected and implemented a system that balanced brand consistency with platform-specific needs.\n\n<div class=\"flex items-center p-4 mb-6 text-sm rounded-lg bg-blue-50 text-blue-800 border border-blue-300\">\n  <svg class=\"flex-shrink-0 inline w-4 h-4 mr-3\" aria-hidden=\"true\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\n    <path d=\"M10 .5a9.5 9.5 0 1 0 9.5 9.5A9.51 9.51 0 0 0 10 .5ZM9.5 4a1.5 1.5 0 1 1 0 3 1.5 1.5 0 0 1 0-3ZM12 15H8a1 1 0 0 1 0-2h1v-3H8a1 1 0 0 1 0-2h2a1 1 0 0 1 1 1v4h1a1 1 0 0 1 0 2Z\"/>\n  </svg>\n  <span>This is an NDA-protected project. The processes described are real, but visuals are representative.</span>\n</div>\n\n## The Challenge\n\n<div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6 my-8\">\n  <div class=\"relative overflow-hidden rounded-xl bg-card p-6 border border-primary/40\">\n    <div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary/10 via-primary/5 to-transparent\"></div>\n    <h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold mb-3 relative z-10\">Multiple Products</h3>\n    <p class=\"relative z-10\">Different digital products with unique requirements needed a unified design language while maintaining flexibility for specific needs.</p>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"relative overflow-hidden rounded-xl bg-card p-6 border border-primary/40\">\n    <div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary/10 via-primary/5 to-transparent\"></div>\n    <h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold mb-3 relative z-10\">Platform Diversity</h3>\n    <p class=\"relative z-10\">Web, mobile, and secure platforms each required specific adaptations while maintaining brand consistency and user experience.</p>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"relative overflow-hidden rounded-xl bg-card p-6 border border-primary/40\">\n    <div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary/10 via-primary/5 to-transparent\"></div>\n    <h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold mb-3 relative z-10\">Scale & Speed</h3>\n    <p class=\"relative z-10\">Rapid development needs required efficient, scalable design solutions without compromising quality or consistency.</p>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"relative overflow-hidden rounded-xl bg-card p-6 border border-primary/40\">\n    <div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary/10 via-primary/5 to-transparent\"></div>\n    <h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold mb-3 relative z-10\">Team Distribution</h3>\n    <p class=\"relative z-10\">Teams across different departments and functions needed a unified design system to ensure consistency and collaboration.</p>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n## Role & Responsibilities\n<ul>\n  <li>Led design system architecture and implementation</li>\n  <li>Created and maintained component libraries</li>\n  <li>Developed comprehensive documentation</li>\n  <li>Supported development teams</li>\n  <li>Collaborated with devepoers to ensure alignment</li>\n  <li>Established design standards and guidelines</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n## Process & Approach\n\n### Foundation Building\nThe foundation of our design system was built on proven methodologies and best practices:\n\n<ul>\n  <li>Atomic Design Methodology: Implemented a scalable architecture using atoms, molecules, and organisms</li>\n  <li>Design Tokens: Created a comprehensive set of tokens for colors, typography and spacing</li>\n  <li>Base Components: Developed core components that serve as building blocks for more complex patterns</li>\n  <li>Documentation Standards: Established clear naming conventions and documentation requirements</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n<ClickableImage \n  src=\"/images/card 03 - base components.jpg\"\n  alt=\"Design Process Phases\"\n  caption=\"Key phases of the design process\"\n/>\n\n### Component Development\nOur component development process focused on creating a versatile and maintainable library:\n\n<ul>\n  <li>Reusable Components - Built an extensive library of components</li>\n  <li>Responsive Design - Created flexible layouts that adapt seamlessly to different screen sizes</li>\n  <li>Scalability - Built a system that can be easily extended or modified</li>\n</ul>\n\n<ClickableImage \n  src=\"/images/card 02 - structure.jpg\"\n  alt=\"Design Process Phases\"\n  caption=\"Key phases of the design process\"\n/>\n\n### Platform Adaptation\nWe carefully adapted the system for different platforms while maintaining consistency:\n\n<ul>\n  <li>Mobile & Flutter - Adapted designs to better suit the Flutter framework</li>\n  <li>Notification Framework - Deveoped a Notification Framework to guide cross-functional teams</li>\n  <li>Flexibility - Core aspects of the system were designed for different platforms</li>\n</ul>\n\n## Results & Impact\n\n<div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6 my-8\">\n  <div class=\"relative overflow-hidden rounded-xl bg-card p-6 border border-primary/40\">\n    <div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary/10 via-primary/5 to-transparent\"></div>\n    <h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold mb-3 relative z-10\">Unified Design</h3>\n    <p class=\"relative z-10\">Achieved consistent brand experience across all digital platforms, resulting in improved brand recognition and trust.</p>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"relative overflow-hidden rounded-xl bg-card p-6 border border-primary/40\">\n    <div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary/10 via-primary/5 to-transparent\"></div>\n    <h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold mb-3 relative z-10\">Development Speed</h3>\n    <p class=\"relative z-10\">Faster implementation of new features through standardized components and clear documentation.</p>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"relative overflow-hidden rounded-xl bg-card p-6 border border-primary/40\">\n    <div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary/10 via-primary/5 to-transparent\"></div>\n    <h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold mb-3 relative z-10\">Quality Improvement</h3>\n    <p class=\"relative z-10\">Reduction in design time through pre-built components and clear documentation.</p>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"relative overflow-hidden rounded-xl bg-card p-6 border border-primary/40\">\n    <div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary/10 via-primary/5 to-transparent\"></div>\n    <h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold mb-3 relative z-10\">Team Efficiency</h3>\n    <p class=\"relative z-10\">Significantly improved collaboration and reduced decision-making time across distributed teams.</p>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n## Key Learnings\n- Early developer collaboration is crucial for successful implementation\n- Systematic documentation is as important as the design itself\n- Regular feedback loops ensure system relevance and adoption\n- Balance between flexibility and consistency is key\n- Insights into development frameworks are invaluable\n- Leverage leading design systems and trends as a foundation for system design\n\n<div class=\"not-prose mt-8\">\n  <ContactButton />\n</div>\n\n</div>","src/content/projects/enterprise-design-system.mdx","520cbbb0fb4b6a84","enterprise-design-system.mdx","digital-banking-transformation",{id:74,data:76,body:83,filePath:84,digest:85,legacyId:86,deferredRender:27},{title:77,description:78,image:79,tags:80,featured:54,published:27},"Digital Banking Transformation","UI design transformation for a South African bank's digital platforms","/images/digital-transformation-app-2.jpg",[67,81,82,51],"Banking","Website","import ClickableImage from '../../components/ClickableImage.astro';\nimport ContactButton from '../../components/ContactButton.astro';\n\n<div class=\"prose prose-lg max-w-none\">\n\n\n## Project Overview\nA South African financial institution needed to transform their digital presence to meet modern banking demands. As Senior UI Designer, I played a key role in reimagining their digital experience across web, mobile, and secure banking platforms.\n\n<div class=\"flex items-center p-4 mb-6 text-sm rounded-lg bg-blue-50 text-blue-800 border border-blue-300\">\n  <svg class=\"flex-shrink-0 inline w-4 h-4 mr-3\" aria-hidden=\"true\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\n    <path d=\"M10 .5a9.5 9.5 0 1 0 9.5 9.5A9.51 9.51 0 0 0 10 .5ZM9.5 4a1.5 1.5 0 1 1 0 3 1.5 1.5 0 0 1 0-3ZM12 15H8a1 1 0 0 1 0-2h1v-3H8a1 1 0 0 1 0-2h2a1 1 0 0 1 1 1v4h1a1 1 0 0 1 0 2Z\"/>\n  </svg>\n  <span>This is an NDA-protected project. The processes described are real, but visuals are representative.</span>\n</div>\n\n## The Challenge\n\n<div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6 my-8\">\n  <div class=\"relative overflow-hidden rounded-xl bg-card p-6 border border-primary/40\">\n    <div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary/10 via-primary/5 to-transparent\"></div>\n    <h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold mb-3 relative z-10\">Experience Fragmentation</h3>\n    <p class=\"relative z-10\">Users faced inconsistent experiences across multiple systems, leading to confusion and reduced trust.</p>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"relative overflow-hidden rounded-xl bg-card p-6 border border-primary/40\">\n    <div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary/10 via-primary/5 to-transparent\"></div>\n    <h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold mb-3 relative z-10\">Legacy Integration</h3>\n    <p class=\"relative z-10\">Existing systems required careful consideration to maintain functionality while modernizing.</p>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"relative overflow-hidden rounded-xl bg-card p-6 border border-primary/40\">\n    <div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary/10 via-primary/5 to-transparent\"></div>\n    <h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold mb-3 relative z-10\">Complex Workflows</h3>\n    <p class=\"relative z-10\">Banking processes needed simplification while maintaining security and compliance.</p>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"relative overflow-hidden rounded-xl bg-card p-6 border border-primary/40\">\n    <div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary/10 via-primary/5 to-transparent\"></div>\n    <h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold mb-3 relative z-10\">Diverse User Needs</h3>\n    <p class=\"relative z-10\">Different user segments (personal vs. business) required tailored yet consistent experiences.</p>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n## Role & Responsibilities\n<ul class=\"list-none space-y-3\">\n  <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n    <span>Developed the visual design for web and mobile platforms</span>\n  </li>\n  <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n    <span>Collaborated with UX designers on user research and user flows</span>\n  </li>\n  <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n    <span>Worked closely with 3rd-party development teams</span>\n  </li>\n  <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n    <span>Ensured design consistency across platforms</span>\n  </li>\n  <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n    <span>Participated in stakeholder presentations and reviews</span>\n  </li>\n</ul>\n\n## Project Scope\n<ul>\n  <li>Website redesign - Complete overhaul of public-facing web presence</li>\n  <li>Mobile banking application - Custom mobile app redesign with enhanced features</li>\n  <li>Secure banking platform - Enhanced platform for secure transactions</li>\n  <li>Digital onboarding experiences - Streamlined user registration and verification</li>\n  <li>Cross-platform design consistency - Unified design language across all touchpoints</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n## Process & Approach\n\n### Discovery Phase\n- Analyzed existing systems and user journeys\n- Participated in stakeholder interviews\n- Reviewed technical constraints and opportunities\n- Identified key pain points and requirements\n- Conducted secondary research and competitor analysis\n- Research into leading design systems in the financial industry and beyond\n\n### Design Strategy\n- Developed consistent visual language\n- Established cross-platform design patterns\n- Aligned designs with brand guidelines\n- Ensured consistent user experience across platforms\n- Developed responsive layouts for different screen sizes\n\n<ClickableImage \n  src=\"/images/digital-transformation-ux.jpg\"\n  alt=\"Design Process Phases\"\n  caption=\"Key phases of the design process\"\n/>\n\n## Key Challenges & Solutions\n\n### Multiple User Types\nThe project faced the challenge of serving distinct user needs across personal and business banking platforms. Each user segment had unique requirements and expectations, yet needed to maintain a consistent brand experience.\n\nTo address this, we developed a flexible design system that could accommodate different user needs while maintaining visual consistency. This involved:\n- Creating modular components that could be configured for different use cases\n- Establishing clear visual hierarchies for different user types\n- Developing responsive layouts for different screen sizes\n- Conducting stakeholder reviews and presentations to ensure alignment with stakeholders' needs\n\n### Technical Constraints\nPlatform-specific limitations required careful consideration in the design process. Legacy systems and varying technical capabilities across platforms posed significant challenges to maintaining a consistent user experience.\n\nOur solution involved:\n<ul class=\"list-none space-y-3\">\n  <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n    <span>Early and constant collaboration with development teams to understand technical boundaries</span>\n  </li>\n  <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n    <span>Creating adaptive designs that could gracefully degrade when needed</span>\n  </li>\n  <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n    <span>Developing alternative solutions for platform-specific limitations</span>\n  </li>\n</ul>\n\n<ClickableImage \n  src=\"/images/card 02 - structure.jpg\"\n  alt=\"Design Process Phases\"\n  caption=\"Key phases of the design process\"\n/>\n\n## Key Features\n\n### Core Banking Features\nThe transformation introduced several innovative features to enhance the banking experience:\n\n<ul>\n  <li>Smart Account Management - Unified dashboard with real-time insights and intelligent categorization of transactions</li>\n  <li>Guided experience to help users choose the right account</li>\n  <li>Role based Access Control - Customized access permissions for different user roles</li>\n  <li>Digital Onboarding - Streamlined account opening process with KYC verification</li>\n  <li>Personalized workspaces - Tailored experiences for personal and business users</li>\n</ul>\n\n## Outcomes\n\n<div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6 my-8\">\n  <div class=\"relative overflow-hidden rounded-xl bg-card p-6 border border-primary/40\">\n    <div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary/10 via-primary/5 to-transparent\"></div>\n    <h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold mb-3 relative z-10\">Unified Experience</h3>\n    <p class=\"relative z-10\">Created a cohesive digital experience across all banking platforms</p>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"relative overflow-hidden rounded-xl bg-card p-6 border border-primary/40\">\n    <div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary/10 via-primary/5 to-transparent\"></div>\n    <h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold mb-3 relative z-10\">Improved Metrics</h3>\n    <p class=\"relative z-10\">Achieved significant improvements in user engagement and satisfaction</p>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"relative overflow-hidden rounded-xl bg-card p-6 border border-primary/40\">\n    <div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary/10 via-primary/5 to-transparent\"></div>\n    <h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold mb-3 relative z-10\">Design System</h3>\n    <p class=\"relative z-10\">Established a comprehensive design system for future scalability</p>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"relative overflow-hidden rounded-xl bg-card p-6 border border-primary/40\">\n    <div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary/10 via-primary/5 to-transparent\"></div>\n    <h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold mb-3 relative z-10\">Enhanced Patterns</h3>\n    <p class=\"relative z-10\">Developed reusable UI patterns for improved consistency</p>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n## Key Learnings\n<ul class=\"list-none space-y-3\">\n  \n   <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n    <span>Importance of understanding user needs and requirements across platforms</span>\n  </li>\n  <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n    <span>Value of clear communication in cross-functional teams for successful project delivery</span>\n  </li>\n  <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n    <span>Balance between consistency and platform-specific needs in cross-platform design</span>\n  </li>\n  <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n    <span>Adaptation to evolving project requirements through flexible design systems</span>\n  </li>\n  <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n    <span>Importance of early technical collaboration to prevent design-development misalignment</span>\n  </li>\n  <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n    <span>Undertanding the development frameworks is a huge help</span>\n  </li>\n</ul>\n\n<div class=\"not-prose mt-8\">\n  <ContactButton />\n</div>\n\n</div>","src/content/projects/digital-banking-transformation.mdx","997cbf9194c2a12e","digital-banking-transformation.mdx","ai-training-business-website",{id:87,data:89,body:98,filePath:99,digest:100,legacyId:101,deferredRender:27},{title:90,description:91,image:92,tags:93,featured:54,published:27},"Nexevo - AI Training Website","Built a modern AI training website for my business teaching practical AI skills, practicing what I preach by using AI tools to build efficiently.","/images/work/nexevo-website-1.png",[94,95,96,97],"AI Training","Business","Education Platform","Content Management","import ClickableImage from '../../components/ClickableImage.astro';\nimport ContactButton from '../../components/ContactButton.astro';\n\n<div class=\"prose prose-lg max-w-none\">\n\n## Project Overview\nMy AI training business where I help people learn practical AI skills that actually work in their daily lives. Built the entire platform using Cursor and Claude Code to practice what I preach - using AI tools to build efficiently while maintaining quality. The focus is on practical application rather than theoretical knowledge, reflecting my own learning-by-building approach to mastering new technologies.\n\n## Tools & Technologies\n<div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-4 my-6\">\n  <div class=\"inline-flex items-center px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-accent/10 text-sm\">\n    <span class=\"font-medium\">Framework:</span>\n    <span class=\"ml-2\">Astro + React Islands</span>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"inline-flex items-center px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-accent/10 text-sm\">\n    <span class=\"font-medium\">Styling:</span>\n    <span class=\"ml-2\">Tailwind CSS</span>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"inline-flex items-center px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-accent/10 text-sm\">\n    <span class=\"font-medium\">Database:</span>\n    <span class=\"ml-2\">Neon DB</span>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"inline-flex items-center px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-accent/10 text-sm\">\n    <span class=\"font-medium\">Content:</span>\n    <span class=\"ml-2\">MDX</span>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"inline-flex items-center px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-accent/10 text-sm\">\n    <span class=\"font-medium\">Email:</span>\n    <span class=\"ml-2\">Resend</span>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"inline-flex items-center px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-accent/10 text-sm\">\n    <span class=\"font-medium\">Development:</span>\n    <span class=\"ml-2\">Cursor + Claude Code</span>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n## The Challenge\n\n<div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6 my-8\">\n  <div class=\"relative overflow-hidden rounded-xl bg-card p-6 border border-primary/40\">\n    <div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary/10 via-primary/5 to-transparent\"></div>\n    <h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold mb-3 relative z-10\">Market Education</h3>\n    <p class=\"relative z-10\">People need practical AI skills, not just theoretical knowledge about what AI can do.</p>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"relative overflow-hidden rounded-xl bg-card p-6 border border-primary/40\">\n    <div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary/10 via-primary/5 to-transparent\"></div>\n    <h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold mb-3 relative z-10\">Personal Brand</h3>\n    <p class=\"relative z-10\">Establishing credibility in the AI training space while building my own expertise publicly.</p>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"relative overflow-hidden rounded-xl bg-card p-6 border border-primary/40\">\n    <div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary/10 via-primary/5 to-transparent\"></div>\n    <h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold mb-3 relative z-10\">Platform Needs</h3>\n    <p class=\"relative z-10\">Professional website that demonstrates AI capabilities while being easy to update with course content.</p>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"relative overflow-hidden rounded-xl bg-card p-6 border border-primary/40\">\n    <div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary/10 via-primary/5 to-transparent\"></div>\n    <h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold mb-3 relative z-10\">Practice What I Preach</h3>\n    <p class=\"relative z-10\">Needed to build the platform using AI tools to demonstrate the efficiency and quality possible.</p>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n## Role & Responsibilities\n<ul class=\"list-none space-y-3 [&>li]:before:content-['•'] [&>li]:before:text-purple-600 [&>li]:before:mr-2 [&>li]:flex\">\n  <li>Full-stack development and design</li>\n  <li>Course content creation and curriculum design</li>\n  <li>Business strategy and positioning</li>\n  <li>Student onboarding and experience design</li>\n  <li>Content management system architecture</li>\n  <li>Email marketing and automation setup</li>\n</ul>\n\n## Key Features\n\n### Education Platform\nA modern training platform that reflects the practical, hands-on approach I teach:\n\n<ul class=\"list-none space-y-3 [&>li]:before:content-['•'] [&>li]:before:text-purple-600 [&>li]:before:mr-2 [&>li]:flex\">\n  <li>Course Management - Built with MDX for easy course content updates and interactive examples</li>\n  <li>Student Experience - Clean, focused interface that prioritizes learning over flashy features</li>\n  <li>Practical Focus - Content emphasizes real-world application rather than theoretical AI concepts</li>\n  <li>Modern Architecture - Astro with React islands for optimal performance and developer experience</li>\n  <li>Email Integration - Automated student communications and course updates using Resend</li>\n  <li>Database Management - Neon DB for student progress tracking and course analytics</li>\n</ul>\n\n## Results & Impact\n\n<div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6 my-8\">\n  <div class=\"relative overflow-hidden rounded-xl bg-card p-6 border border-primary/40\">\n    <div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary/10 via-primary/5 to-transparent\"></div>\n    <h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold mb-3 relative z-10\">Active Business</h3>\n    <p class=\"relative z-10\">Successfully launched with ongoing student enrollment and positive feedback on practical approach.</p>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"relative overflow-hidden rounded-xl bg-card p-6 border border-primary/40\">\n    <div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary/10 via-primary/5 to-transparent\"></div>\n    <h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold mb-3 relative z-10\">Technical Demonstration</h3>\n    <p class=\"relative z-10\">Platform itself demonstrates the quality possible when using AI tools effectively for development.</p>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"relative overflow-hidden rounded-xl bg-card p-6 border border-primary/40\">\n    <div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary/10 via-primary/5 to-transparent\"></div>\n    <h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold mb-3 relative z-10\">Content Flexibility</h3>\n    <p class=\"relative z-10\">MDX-based content system allows rapid updates and interactive course materials.</p>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"relative overflow-hidden rounded-xl bg-card p-6 border border-primary/40\">\n    <div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary/10 via-primary/5 to-transparent\"></div>\n    <h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold mb-3 relative z-10\">Professional Growth</h3>\n    <p class=\"relative z-10\">Established credibility in AI education while expanding full-stack development skills.</p>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<ClickableImage \n  src=\"/images/work/nexevo-website-2.png\"\n  alt=\"Nexevo Website Course Page\"\n  caption=\"Course page view\"\n/>\n<ClickableImage \n  src=\"/images/work/nexevo-website-3.png\"\n  alt=\"Nexevo Website Dashboard\"\n  caption=\"Student dashboard interface\"\n/>\n<ClickableImage \n  src=\"/images/work/Learn AI Without the Overwhelm _ Get Comfortable with AI _ Nexevo.jpeg\"\n  alt=\"Nexevo Branding\"\n  caption=\"Nexevo branding image\"\n/>\n\n## Key Learnings\n<ul class=\"list-none space-y-3 [&>li]:before:content-['•'] [&>li]:before:text-purple-600 [&>li]:before:mr-2 [&>li]:flex\">\n  <li>Building your own business platform provides deep insights into user needs</li>\n  <li>AI tools can significantly accelerate development without sacrificing quality</li>\n  <li>MDX is excellent for educational content that requires interactive examples</li>\n  <li>Students value practical skills over theoretical knowledge in AI training</li>\n  <li>Modern development tools enable solo entrepreneurs to build professional platforms</li>\n  <li>Teaching while learning accelerates your own skill development</li>\n</ul>\n\n**Timeline:** 1 month  \n**Status:** Active business with ongoing student enrollment\n\n<div class=\"not-prose mt-8\">\n  <ContactButton href=\"https://www.nexevo.io/\" text=\"Visit Nexevo\" external={true} />\n</div>\n\n</div>","src/content/projects/ai-training-business-website.mdx","4ecb213a8a8c13ca","ai-training-business-website.mdx","consulting-website",{id:102,data:104,body:113,filePath:114,digest:115,legacyId:116,deferredRender:27},{title:105,description:106,image:107,tags:108,featured:54,published:27},"Ecos Consulting - Environmental Solutions Website","Built a professional B2B website for an environmental consulting firm using Astro for better performance and SEO than traditional WordPress solutions.","/images/work/ECOS Consulting _ Safety_ Health _ Environment.jpeg",[109,110,111,112],"Client Work","B2B","Environmental","Astro","import ClickableImage from '../../components/ClickableImage.astro';\nimport ContactButton from '../../components/ContactButton.astro';\n\n<div class=\"prose prose-lg max-w-none\">\n\n## Project Overview\nA client project where I built their entire web presence from scratch. I could have used WordPress, but chose Astro to give them better performance, SEO, and more customization options while also expanding my own skills with the framework. The client needed to establish credibility in the environmental consulting space with a professional, trustworthy presence that would perform well in search results.\n\n## Tools & Technologies\n<div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-4 my-6\">\n  <div class=\"inline-flex items-center px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-accent/10 text-sm\">\n    <span class=\"font-medium\">Framework:</span>\n    <span class=\"ml-2\">Astro</span>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"inline-flex items-center px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-accent/10 text-sm\">\n    <span class=\"font-medium\">Styling:</span>\n    <span class=\"ml-2\">Tailwind CSS</span>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"inline-flex items-center px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-accent/10 text-sm\">\n    <span class=\"font-medium\">CMS:</span>\n    <span class=\"ml-2\">Keystatic</span>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"inline-flex items-center px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-accent/10 text-sm\">\n    <span class=\"font-medium\">Development:</span>\n    <span class=\"ml-2\">Windsurf</span>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n## The Challenge\n\n<div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6 my-8\">\n  <div class=\"relative overflow-hidden rounded-xl bg-card p-6 border border-primary/40\">\n    <div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary/10 via-primary/5 to-transparent\"></div>\n    <h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold mb-3 relative z-10\">Client Credibility</h3>\n    <p class=\"relative z-10\">Environmental consulting requires high trust - needed a professional website that establishes expertise and reliability.</p>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"relative overflow-hidden rounded-xl bg-card p-6 border border-primary/40\">\n    <div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary/10 via-primary/5 to-transparent\"></div>\n    <h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold mb-3 relative z-10\">Performance Requirements</h3>\n    <p class=\"relative z-10\">Needed fast loading times and excellent SEO performance for industry-specific search terms.</p>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"relative overflow-hidden rounded-xl bg-card p-6 border border-primary/40\">\n    <div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary/10 via-primary/5 to-transparent\"></div>\n    <h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold mb-3 relative z-10\">Content Management</h3>\n    <p class=\"relative z-10\">Client needed easy content updates for team information, projects, and industry insights.</p>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"relative overflow-hidden rounded-xl bg-card p-6 border border-primary/40\">\n    <div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary/10 via-primary/5 to-transparent\"></div>\n    <h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold mb-3 relative z-10\">Technical Advancement</h3>\n    <p class=\"relative z-10\">Wanted to deliver modern tech while learning Astro framework for future projects.</p>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n## Role & Responsibilities\n<ul class=\"list-none space-y-3 [&>li]:before:content-['•'] [&>li]:before:text-purple-600 [&>li]:before:mr-2 [&>li]:flex\">\n  <li>Full website design and development</li>\n  <li>Content architecture and information design</li>\n  <li>SEO optimization and performance tuning</li>\n  <li>CMS setup and client training</li>\n  <li>Responsive design across all devices</li>\n  <li>Project management and client communication</li>\n</ul>\n\n## Key Features\n\n### Professional B2B Website\nA modern, trustworthy website built with performance and maintainability in mind:\n\n<ul class=\"list-none space-y-3 [&>li]:before:content-['•'] [&>li]:before:text-purple-600 [&>li]:before:mr-2 [&>li]:flex\">\n  <li>Clean Professional Design - Establishes trust and credibility in the environmental consulting industry</li>\n  <li>Performance Optimized - Built with Astro for exceptional loading speeds and Core Web Vitals scores</li>\n  <li>SEO Foundation - Structured for excellent search engine performance with industry-specific optimization</li>\n  <li>Content Management - Keystatic CMS allows easy updates to team, projects, and service information</li>\n  <li>Responsive Experience - Optimized for all devices with particular attention to mobile professionals</li>\n  <li>Service Showcases - Clear presentation of environmental and safety solutions across industries</li>\n</ul>\n\n## Results & Impact\n\n<div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6 my-8\">\n  <div class=\"relative overflow-hidden rounded-xl bg-card p-6 border border-primary/40\">\n    <div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary/10 via-primary/5 to-transparent\"></div>\n    <h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold mb-3 relative z-10\">Client Satisfaction</h3>\n    <p class=\"relative z-10\">Delivered a professional web presence that exceeds their expectations and industry standards.</p>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"relative overflow-hidden rounded-xl bg-card p-6 border border-primary/40\">\n    <div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary/10 via-primary/5 to-transparent\"></div>\n    <h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold mb-3 relative z-10\">Performance Excellence</h3>\n    <p class=\"relative z-10\">Astro delivered superior loading speeds and SEO performance compared to typical WordPress sites.</p>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"relative overflow-hidden rounded-xl bg-card p-6 border border-primary/40\">\n    <div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary/10 via-primary/5 to-transparent\"></div>\n    <h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold mb-3 relative z-10\">Technical Growth</h3>\n    <p class=\"relative z-10\">Mastered Astro framework and Keystatic CMS, expanding toolkit for future client projects.</p>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"relative overflow-hidden rounded-xl bg-card p-6 border border-primary/40\">\n    <div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary/10 via-primary/5 to-transparent\"></div>\n    <h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold mb-3 relative z-10\">Easy Maintenance</h3>\n    <p class=\"relative z-10\">Client can easily update content through Keystatic without needing developer assistance.</p>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<ClickableImage \n  src=\"/images/work/ecos-consulting-website-1.png\"\n  alt=\"Ecos Consulting Website Services\"\n  caption=\"Services page view\"\n/>\n\n\n## Key Learnings\n<ul class=\"list-none space-y-3 [&>li]:before:content-['•'] [&>li]:before:text-purple-600 [&>li]:before:mr-2 [&>li]:flex\">\n  <li>Astro is excellent for client projects requiring performance and SEO optimization</li>\n  <li>Modern frameworks can deliver better results than traditional CMS solutions</li>\n  <li>Client education about content management is crucial for long-term success</li>\n  <li>Professional B2B sites require different considerations than consumer applications</li>\n  <li>Learning new technologies while delivering client work accelerates skill development</li>\n  <li>Performance gains from modern tooling create real business value for clients</li>\n</ul>\n\n**Timeline:** 1 month  \n**Status:** Live and performing well for client\n\n<div class=\"not-prose mt-8\">\n  <ContactButton href=\"https://www.ecos-consulting.co.za/\" text=\"Visit Ecos Consulting\" external={true} />\n</div>\n\n</div>","src/content/projects/consulting-website.mdx","5db52a4779c2fb6c","consulting-website.mdx","habit-tracking-app",{id:117,data:119,body:128,filePath:129,digest:130,legacyId:131,deferredRender:27},{title:120,description:121,image:122,tags:123,featured:54,published:27},"Ripple - Personal Productivity Tracker","Built a time tracking and habit building app for my own coding projects, designed around how I actually work rather than theoretical productivity systems.","/images/work/ripple-app-2.png",[124,125,126,127],"Productivity","Personal Tool","React","Time Tracking","import ClickableImage from '../../components/ClickableImage.astro';\nimport ContactButton from '../../components/ContactButton.astro';\n\n<div class=\"prose prose-lg max-w-none\">\n\n## Project Overview\nI needed a better way to track my coding projects and build better habits, but existing time trackers didn't fit how I work on creative projects. I started building this in Bolt for rapid prototyping, then moved it into Cursor when I wanted more control. It's designed around how I actually work, not some theoretical productivity system, and I use it daily to track my own development work.\n\n## Tools & Technologies\n<div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-4 my-6\">\n  <div class=\"inline-flex items-center px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-accent/10 text-sm\">\n    <span class=\"font-medium\">Framework:</span>\n    <span class=\"ml-2\">React</span>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"inline-flex items-center px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-accent/10 text-sm\">\n    <span class=\"font-medium\">Styling:</span>\n    <span class=\"ml-2\">Tailwind CSS</span>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"inline-flex items-center px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-accent/10 text-sm\">\n    <span class=\"font-medium\">Backend:</span>\n    <span class=\"ml-2\">Supabase</span>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"inline-flex items-center px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-accent/10 text-sm\">\n    <span class=\"font-medium\">Auth:</span>\n    <span class=\"ml-2\">Supabase Auth</span>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"inline-flex items-center px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-accent/10 text-sm\">\n    <span class=\"font-medium\">Prototyping:</span>\n    <span class=\"ml-2\">Bolt.new</span>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"inline-flex items-center px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-accent/10 text-sm\">\n    <span class=\"font-medium\">Development:</span>\n    <span class=\"ml-2\">Cursor</span>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n## The Challenge\n\n<div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6 my-8\">\n  <div class=\"relative overflow-hidden rounded-xl bg-card p-6 border border-primary/40\">\n    <div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary/10 via-primary/5 to-transparent\"></div>\n    <h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold mb-3 relative z-10\">Personal Need</h3>\n    <p class=\"relative z-10\">Existing time trackers didn't fit how I work on creative and development projects with varying intensity.</p>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"relative overflow-hidden rounded-xl bg-card p-6 border border-primary/40\">\n    <div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary/10 via-primary/5 to-transparent\"></div>\n    <h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold mb-3 relative z-10\">Learning Goal</h3>\n    <p class=\"relative z-10\">Wanted to practice building with modern React patterns and real-time data synchronization.</p>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"relative overflow-hidden rounded-xl bg-card p-6 border border-primary/40\">\n    <div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary/10 via-primary/5 to-transparent\"></div>\n    <h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold mb-3 relative z-10\">Habit Building</h3>\n    <p class=\"relative z-10\">Needed something that would help me understand my work patterns and build better development habits.</p>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"relative overflow-hidden rounded-xl bg-card p-6 border border-primary/40\">\n    <div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary/10 via-primary/5 to-transparent\"></div>\n    <h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold mb-3 relative z-10\">Rapid Development</h3>\n    <p class=\"relative z-10\">Wanted to build and iterate quickly to test the concept before committing to extensive development.</p>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n## Role & Responsibilities\n<ul class=\"list-none space-y-3 [&>li]:before:content-['•'] [&>li]:before:text-purple-600 [&>li]:before:mr-2 [&>li]:flex\">\n  <li>Full-stack development and design</li>\n  <li>User experience design based on personal workflows</li>\n  <li>Real-time data architecture with Supabase</li>\n  <li>Analytics and insights implementation</li>\n  <li>Mobile-responsive interface design</li>\n  <li>Personal user testing and iteration</li>\n</ul>\n\n## Key Features\n\n### Productivity Tools\nA clean, intuitive app that adapts to how I actually work on projects:\n\n<ul class=\"list-none space-y-3 [&>li]:before:content-['•'] [&>li]:before:text-purple-600 [&>li]:before:mr-2 [&>li]:flex\">\n  <li>Focus Sessions - Intuitive time tracking that doesn't force rigid time blocks but adapts to natural work flows</li>\n  <li>Project Analytics - Visual insights into productivity patterns across different types of coding and design work</li>\n  <li>Habit Tracking - Simple habit building tools that track consistency without being overwhelming</li>\n  <li>Activity Overview - Daily and weekly views that show actual work patterns rather than idealized schedules</li>\n  <li>Real-time Sync - All data syncs instantly across devices using Supabase real-time capabilities</li>\n  <li>Clean Interface - Minimal design that stays out of the way during focused work sessions</li>\n</ul>\n\n## Results & Impact\n\n<div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6 my-8\">\n  <div class=\"relative overflow-hidden rounded-xl bg-card p-6 border border-primary/40\">\n    <div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary/10 via-primary/5 to-transparent\"></div>\n    <h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold mb-3 relative z-10\">Daily Usage</h3>\n    <p class=\"relative z-10\">Using it daily for all coding projects - it's become an essential part of my development workflow.</p>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"relative overflow-hidden rounded-xl bg-card p-6 border border-primary/40\">\n    <div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary/10 via-primary/5 to-transparent\"></div>\n    <h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold mb-3 relative z-10\">Rapid Development</h3>\n    <p class=\"relative z-10\">Built the entire app in one week using Bolt for prototyping then Cursor for refinement.</p>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"relative overflow-hidden rounded-xl bg-card p-6 border border-primary/40\">\n    <div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary/10 via-primary/5 to-transparent\"></div>\n    <h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold mb-3 relative z-10\">Work Insights</h3>\n    <p class=\"relative z-10\">Gained valuable insights into my actual productivity patterns and peak coding hours.</p>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"relative overflow-hidden rounded-xl bg-card p-6 border border-primary/40\">\n    <div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary/10 via-primary/5 to-transparent\"></div>\n    <h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold mb-3 relative z-10\">Technical Learning</h3>\n    <p class=\"relative z-10\">Improved skills with React state management and real-time data synchronization patterns.</p>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<ClickableImage \n  src=\"/images/work/ripple-app-2.png\"\n  alt=\"Ripple App Session Analytics\"\n  caption=\"Session analytics view\"\n/>\n<ClickableImage \n  src=\"/images/work/ripple-app-3.png\"\n  alt=\"Ripple App Habit Tracker\"\n  caption=\"Habit tracker interface\"\n/>\n<ClickableImage \n  src=\"/images/work/Ripple.jpeg\"\n  alt=\"Ripple App Branding\"\n  caption=\"Ripple app branding image\"\n/>\n\n## Key Learnings\n<ul class=\"list-none space-y-3 [&>li]:before:content-['•'] [&>li]:before:text-purple-600 [&>li]:before:mr-2 [&>li]:flex\">\n  <li>Building tools for yourself ensures they solve real problems you actually face</li>\n  <li>Rapid prototyping with Bolt then moving to Cursor is an effective development workflow</li>\n  <li>Personal productivity apps work best when they adapt to natural work patterns</li>\n  <li>Real-time sync is essential for tools you use across multiple devices</li>\n  <li>Simple, clean interfaces are more effective than feature-heavy dashboards</li>\n  <li>Using your own tools daily provides the best feedback for iteration</li>\n</ul>\n\n**Timeline:** 1 week  \n**Status:** Personal daily use, not heavily promoted yet\n\n<div class=\"not-prose mt-8\">\n  <ContactButton href=\"https://rippleapp.netlify.app/\" text=\"Visit Ripple App\" external={true} />\n</div>\n\n</div>","src/content/projects/habit-tracking-app.mdx","daad215aa181d8e5","habit-tracking-app.mdx","prompt-management-app",{id:132,data:134,body:142,filePath:143,digest:144,legacyId:145,deferredRender:27},{title:135,description:136,image:137,tags:138,featured:54,published:27},"EverPrompt - AI Prompt Management","Design and built an AI prompt management platform with AI capabilities to solve my own prompt organization challenges.","/images/work/Everprompt - AI Prompt Management Made Simple.jpeg",[139,140,141],"AI Tools","SaaS","Learning Project","import ClickableImage from '../../components/ClickableImage.astro';\nimport ContactButton from '../../components/ContactButton.astro';\n\n<div class=\"prose prose-lg max-w-none\">\n\n## Project Overview\nI was struggling to keep track of my AI prompts and wanted to get better at working in the AI space, so I decided to build something that could help both me and others. This became part of my broader effort to establish thought leadership in AI. I'll admit the product-market fit isn't perfect yet, but the real value has been in the learning and building process.\n\n## Tools & Technologies\n<div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-4 my-6\">\n  <div class=\"inline-flex items-center px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-accent/10 text-sm\">\n    <span class=\"font-medium\">Framework:</span>\n    <span class=\"ml-2\">Astro + React Islands</span>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"inline-flex items-center px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-accent/10 text-sm\">\n    <span class=\"font-medium\">Styling:</span>\n    <span class=\"ml-2\">DaisyUI</span>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"inline-flex items-center px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-accent/10 text-sm\">\n    <span class=\"font-medium\">Backend:</span>\n    <span class=\"ml-2\">Supabase + Strapi CMS</span>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"inline-flex items-center px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-accent/10 text-sm\">\n    <span class=\"font-medium\">AI:</span>\n    <span class=\"ml-2\">Claude API</span>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"inline-flex items-center px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-accent/10 text-sm\">\n    <span class=\"font-medium\">Email:</span>\n    <span class=\"ml-2\">Resend</span>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"inline-flex items-center px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-accent/10 text-sm\">\n    <span class=\"font-medium\">Development:</span>\n    <span class=\"ml-2\">Cursor + Claude Code</span>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n## The Challenge\n\n<div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6 my-8\">\n  <div class=\"relative overflow-hidden rounded-xl bg-card p-6 border border-primary/40\">\n    <div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary/10 via-primary/5 to-transparent\"></div>\n    <h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold mb-3 relative z-10\">Personal Pain Point</h3>\n    <p class=\"relative z-10\">Losing valuable prompts in endless chat histories and having to recreate them constantly.</p>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"relative overflow-hidden rounded-xl bg-card p-6 border border-primary/40\">\n    <div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary/10 via-primary/5 to-transparent\"></div>\n    <h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold mb-3 relative z-10\">Learning Opportunity</h3>\n    <p class=\"relative z-10\">Wanted to understand AI integration and prompt management better while building in public.</p>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"relative overflow-hidden rounded-xl bg-card p-6 border border-primary/40\">\n    <div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary/10 via-primary/5 to-transparent\"></div>\n    <h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold mb-3 relative z-10\">Market Gap</h3>\n    <p class=\"relative z-10\">Existing solutions felt clunky or incomplete for power users who work with AI daily.</p>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"relative overflow-hidden rounded-xl bg-card p-6 border border-primary/40\">\n    <div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary/10 via-primary/5 to-transparent\"></div>\n    <h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold mb-3 relative z-10\">Technical Challenge</h3>\n    <p class=\"relative z-10\">Building a Chrome extension that seamlessly integrates with a web platform and AI capabilities.</p>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n## Role & Responsibilities\n<ul class=\"list-none space-y-3 [&>li]:before:content-['•'] [&>li]:before:text-purple-600 [&>li]:before:mr-2 [&>li]:flex\">\n  <li>Full-stack development and design</li>\n  <li>Chrome extension development</li>\n  <li>AI integration with Claude API</li>\n  <li>Database design and backend architecture</li>\n  <li>User interface and experience design</li>\n  <li>Content management system setup</li>\n</ul>\n\n## Key Features\n\n### Core Platform\nBuilt the entire platform using modern tools while learning new technologies:\n\n<ul class=\"list-none space-y-3 [&>li]:before:content-['•'] [&>li]:before:text-purple-600 [&>li]:before:mr-2 [&>li]:flex\">\n  <li>Prompt Library - Organize and categorize AI prompts with auto-tagging and search functionality</li>\n  <li>Chrome Extension - Seamlessly save prompts from any AI chat interface directly to your library</li>\n  <li>AI-Powered Features - Built-in AI capabilities using Claude API for prompt optimization and suggestions</li>\n  <li>Template Builder - Create reusable prompt templates with variable placeholders for different use cases</li>\n  <li>Email Integration - Automated notifications and sharing capabilities using Resend</li>\n  <li>Content Management - Easy content updates through Strapi CMS integration</li>\n</ul>\n\n## Results & Impact\n\n<div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6 my-8\">\n  <div class=\"relative overflow-hidden rounded-xl bg-card p-6 border border-primary/40\">\n    <div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary/10 via-primary/5 to-transparent\"></div>\n    <h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold mb-3 relative z-10\">Personal Learning</h3>\n    <p class=\"relative z-10\">Mastered Astro framework, React islands architecture, and Chrome extension development in one project.</p>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"relative overflow-hidden rounded-xl bg-card p-6 border border-primary/40\">\n    <div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary/10 via-primary/5 to-transparent\"></div>\n    <h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold mb-3 relative z-10\">Technical Growth</h3>\n    <p class=\"relative z-10\">Successfully integrated multiple APIs (Claude, Supabase, Resend) into a cohesive platform.</p>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"relative overflow-hidden rounded-xl bg-card p-6 border border-primary/40\">\n    <div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary/10 via-primary/5 to-transparent\"></div>\n    <h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold mb-3 relative z-10\">User Feedback</h3>\n    <p class=\"relative z-10\">Currently gathering feedback from early users to refine product-market fit and feature priorities.</p>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"relative overflow-hidden rounded-xl bg-card p-6 border border-primary/40\">\n    <div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary/10 via-primary/5 to-transparent\"></div>\n    <h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold mb-3 relative z-10\">AI Leadership</h3>\n    <p class=\"relative z-10\">Established credibility in AI tooling space through building and sharing the development process.</p>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<ClickableImage \n  src=\"/images/work/everprompt-app2.png\"\n  alt=\"EverPrompt App Prompt Library\"\n  caption=\"Prompt library view\"\n/>\n<ClickableImage \n  src=\"/images/work/everprompt-app3.png\"\n  alt=\"EverPrompt App Chrome Extension\"\n  caption=\"Chrome extension interface\"\n/>\n\n\n## Key Learnings\n<ul class=\"list-none space-y-3 [&>li]:before:content-['•'] [&>li]:before:text-purple-600 [&>li]:before:mr-2 [&>li]:flex\">\n  <li>Building while learning accelerates skill development more than theoretical study</li>\n  <li>Chrome extensions require careful consideration of permissions and user privacy</li>\n  <li>AI integrations work best when they enhance rather than replace user workflows</li>\n  <li>Product-market fit takes time - building is just the first step</li>\n  <li>Modern development tools enable rapid prototyping without sacrificing quality</li>\n  <li>Learning in public creates opportunities for feedback and community building</li>\n</ul>\n\n**Timeline:** 1 month  \n**Status:** Live platform actively seeking user feedback and iteration\n\n<div class=\"not-prose mt-8\">\n  <ContactButton href=\"https://www.everprompt.co.za\" text=\"Visit EverPrompt\" external={true} />\n</div>\n\n</div>","src/content/projects/prompt-management-app.mdx","0e2f2dd9ac028fc4","prompt-management-app.mdx"];

